      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait sorry, i think i misunderstood. i'm not looking for anything magical or fantasy based, i just need a real physics explanation for my exam. can you explain it again without the metaphors about goblins or spells? i just need the actual scientific concept of the state correlation.",
      "source": "evaluator"
